I always knew I was supposed to be a successful businesswoman. When I was a little girl, I could see the vision so clearly. But overtime, I dimmed my Light to fit into places never built to support who I AM. I stopped advocating for my dreams because people told me I was living in a fantasy world. 

However, in this season of my life, I am giving my Inner Child all that her heart desired 🤍✨I make six figures a year and drive my luxury dream car. I know what’s next for me and I am walking with so much joy into this new era of being. 🦋 None of this would be possible without the book The Silent Feminine Power by Lana Cressel. Life is blessed and the Most High can do the all things! I am grateful to have found your channel!
